Species of the genus Chrysotimus Loew from China (Diptera, Dolichopodidae)Abstract The following three species are described as new to science: Chrysotimus dalongensis sp. n., Chrysotimus huairouensis sp. n., and Chrysotimus hubeiensis sp. n., Chrysotimus apicicurvatus Yang, is recorded from Palaearctic China for the first time. A key to the Chinese species of the genus is presented.